rComments: He was a hilarious teacher. We just had to read a lot of books and stories for this class, but if you did, you were fine. The film project that was worth 30% of our grade was pretty cool.

I actually liked attending class.  If you went and wrote your three short stories, you pretty much got an A.  Plus, he is a very cool teacher and makes discussions enjoyable; he's definitely one of my favorite instructors.
